@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!-- The about page. As of right now the [blanks] are for future problems like a dedicated email for accepting game submissions, feedback, etc. -->

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>At BucStop, our mission is to provide a safe and engaging platform for students to explore, discover, and connect with their interests. We strive to offer a unique experience that fosters creativity, learning, and community engagement.</p>

    <h2>Our Commitment to Copyrighted Material</h2>
    <p>At BucStop, we respect the intellectual property rights of others and expect our users to do the same. We do not tolerate the unauthorized use or distribution of copyrighted material on our platform. If you believe your copyright-protected work has been infringed upon, please contact us immediately at [blank].</p>

    <h2>Our Malware Policy</h2>
    <p>Ensuring the safety and security of our users is paramount at BucStop. We have measures in place to detect and prevent malware from being distributed through our platform. Any attempt to upload or distribute malware will result in immediate removal.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our mission, copyright policy, or malware policy, please contact us at [blank].</p>

    <p>Thank you for being a part of the BucStop community!</p>
</body>
</html>
